#: ../../../reference/maskedarray.generic.rst:410
msgid ""
"When accessing a slice, the output is a masked array whose :attr:"
"`~MaskedArray.data` attribute is a view of the original data, and whose mask "
"is either :attr:`nomask` (if there was no invalid entries in the original "
"array) or a view of the corresponding slice of the original mask. The view "
"is required to ensure propagation of any modification of the mask to the "
"original."
msgstr ""

